snippet: A car bomber detonated explosives at an army checkpoint on a bridge in Anbar Province on Thursday, killing at least 16 people, including security officers and members of a wedding party.
abstract: Car bomber detonates explosives at an army checkpoint on a bridge in Anbar Province, Iraq, killing at least 16 people.
lead_paragraph: A car bomber detonated explosives at an army checkpoint on a bridge in Anbar Province on Thursday, killing at least 16 people, including security officers and members of a wedding party.

headline.main: Iraq: Members of Wedding Party Are Killed in Blast
headline.print_headline: Iraq: Members of Wedding Party Killed in Anbar Blast
